lead_paragraph: Bradley Wright-Phillips scored his 16th goal of the season in the 55th minute and the New York Red Bulls beat the New England Revolution 1-0 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Wright-Phillips Scores 16th Goal, Red Bulls Beat Revs 1-0
